{"tid":1649001,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"on9次次都星期六日出嚟仲要預先講定比對方部署","createTime":"2019-10-12T12:54:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T13:36:09.000Z","uid":217108,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"9c97e323e760d4717c1b8619b97c58169421b422","tid":1649001,"uid":217108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T12:54:38.000Z","msg":"個個星期唔同日子<br />\n仲要勁遲先講出嚟等佢冇得部署<br />\n依家次次都星期六日<br />\n對方星期一至五基本上都係大休息<br />\n基本上抖足精神等你哋假日先出嚟一網打盡<br />\n講真唔定期等佢哋日日都要戒備<br />\n佢哋先會疲於奔命"},{"pid":"a28997e75f1038e3664119cffff1204a7deab7b8","tid":1649001,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T12:55:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9fcc6ed5977d3fda93512992f3a61e41fa97e3f3","tid":1649001,"uid":217108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T12:55:58.000Z","msg":"幫手推比大家知"},{"pid":"93a724265fbc41a5ee6c1205ade0244424abccd3","tid":1649001,"uid":217108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T12:56:12.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"a2caa609fb16ce9104a4dd137b3d6f0420b39125","tid":1649001,"uid":217108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T12:56:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d1d3ae765860c2c553163d52402d759cb388d7b4","tid":1649001,"uid":217108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a2caa609fb16ce9104a4dd137b3d6f0420b39125","tid":1649001,"uid":217108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T12:56:57.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T12:57:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"098d57167ae204bb6589d490e9adabd3f6534f2b","tid":1649001,"uid":217108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T12:57:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"71789fe9fdb0c8214e6efb3d0d6f8c67e284021c","tid":1649001,"uid":217108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T12:57:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"97807cf2174718eb0c95d41bf1907d612a2678f1","tid":1649001,"uid":55851,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score